data.title: League Trophy Hunting Report 2023 Digital2
data.meta_description: league_trophy_hunting_report_2023_digital2 - Read online for free. This report analyzes the extent, scale, and cost of trophy hunting in Great Britain. Trophy hunting is legal and widespread, occurring in at least 23 counties. It is readily available to novices through simple online booking. Trophy hunting targets six deer species and other species, and costs range from £60 to over £952 per outing. However, some providers lack pricing transparency. While trophy hunting is presented as wildlife management, this report questions whether it could distort lethal management priorities.
